author: The Critical Drinker
description: Ever wanted to watch Giancarlo Esposito fighting a giant peanut man in a mech suit? Ever wanted to see Chris Pratt and Millie Bobby Brown struggle through a script that has no idea what to do with them? Then Electric State has got you covered. For everyone else, this $320 Million disaster was an absolute waste of time and huge amounts of money. Join me as I suffer through it for your amusement.
title: The Electric State - A $320 Million Dumpster Fire
